/* —————————————————————————————— //
NAME:
	TextSplit ( text ; splitChar )

PURPOSE:
	Breaks text string on splitChar into return-delimited list.
	Also strips whitespace from ends of each line.

EXAMPLES:
	TextSplit ( "dog, cat ,mouse" ; "," ) = "dog¶cat¶mouse"

HISTORY:
	Created: 2011-Mar-08 09h33 PST — Donovan A. Chandler
*/